                        PORTAGEshared source code

Contents of this directory:

   build/           tools for making and installing
   canoe/           decoder code, including code for using translation models
   eval/            code for automatic evaluation of MT output
   preprocessing/   markup, tokenization, etc.
   rescoring/       nbest list reordering
   lm/              code for using language models
   tm/              code for creating translation models (lexical and phrase based)
   api/             API to the decoder, for including in other applications
   utils/           basic tools for other modules to use
   logging/         logging facility for debugging 
